      "description": "PIV-measured velocity fields and outlet hemolysis index compared against CFD predictions at nominal hardware condition. New pump assembly with factory-fresh bearing. RH = 0.83 (< 1.0 acceptance criterion met). All boundary conditions set to manufacturer nominal values; no fault states introduced."
    },
    {
