      "name": "Bench validation — nominal pump, 3 L/min, 2000 RPM",
      "description": "Hemolysis index measured in vitro using bovine blood at nominal operating point. CFD prediction within 8% of measured RH. Hardware in new condition; motor drive operating at rated voltage with no perturbation."
    },
