      "name": "Bench validation — nominal pump, 4 L/min, 2200 RPM",
      "description": "Validation at intermediate flow-speed combination. Pump assembly inspected and confirmed within dimensional tolerance prior to test. No wear, no electrical fault, no inlet restriction. CFD RH prediction 0.91 vs measured 0.88."
