      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-vr-005-partial-occlusion-single",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Inlet partial-occlusion sensitivity — single restricted condition",
      "description": "One validation run performed with a 15% inlet area restriction to represent tubing kink. CFD and bench results agree within 12% on RH. This single fault-adjacent condition was included to demonstrate model responsiveness to inlet geometry change; it is not representative of the range of physical fault modes (bearing wear, motor-drive sag, electrical transients) encountered in clinical use. No further fault states were exercised in the validation campaign."
    }
