      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must reproduce manufactured-solution benchmark to within 1% L2 error for laminar pipe flow and rotating frame cases.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to rotating-frame Navier-Stokes implementation. L2 velocity error 0.4% at equivalent mesh density to production runs. Second-order spatial convergence confirmed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
