      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error assessed as part of code verification and discretization error factors; standalone iterative convergence monitoring confirms residuals < 1e-5 for all runs. Formal separate factor not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
