      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Simulation workflow executed by experienced CFD analyst with documented SOPs. Independent review of mesh and boundary condition setup performed. Formal use-error assessment not required at MRL 2."
